    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors scoped to not-assessed status consistent with MRL 2 requirements per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. Validation evidence demonstrates RH index agreement within 8.3 % normalised RMS error across all 5 COU operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device within the assessed scenarios.",
